item.title: Jar maker error will rep++
item.dc:creator: @ry60003333 ry60003333
item.description:
@ry60003333 wrote:

Please stop spamming and arguing or I will close the thread.

As far as the error message go, the screenshot you posted doesn’t help because it doesn’t include any actual except, just a list of files that JARMaker was adding to the jar.

A much easier way to make JARs is to put your client into a Netbeans project, see http://netbeans.org .
